10

Set in Stepantsminda, 47 km from Republican Spartak Stadium, Cozy Hotel Kazbegi offers accommodation with a garden, free private parking and a restaurant. This 2-star hotel offers luggage storage space. The accommodation provides karaoke and free WiFi. At the hotel, all rooms are equipped with a wardrobe, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen and towels. The units will provide guests with a minibar.

Couples particularly like the superb location — they rated it 9.4 for a two-person trip.
